quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  12,53,"Mi la…ď…ďinaa hoore-am, tawde woŇčkii ko heewkii yamirde bone, si wanah kiin ki Joomi am yurmini. Joomi am ko jaafotoo…óo jurmotoo…óo."
  12,54,"Laam…óo on wi'i: "ngaddanee kam mo, mi heertinana mo hoore-am". Nde o yewtunoo mo, o wi'i: "Aa on hannde ka amen, ko a jom-nokku koolaa…óo"."
  12,55,"O maaki: "Wa…óam e hoore-ngaluuji leydi ndin: ko mi deenoowo ganndu…óo"."
  12,56,"Ko wano nii min √Īimnirani Yuusufa ka leydi, homo jippora e mayri nokku ka o yi…ói. mi…óen ke…ďnira yurmeende amen nden on mo min muuyi, min njeebataaka njo…ďdi mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe …ďen."
  12,57,"Pellet ko njo…ďdi laakara ndiin …ďuri mo∆ī∆īannde …ďen gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďe laatii gooŇč…óu…ďe."
  12,58,"-Musi…ó…ďe-baaba-gootoo…ďe Yuusufa …ďeen ngari …ďe naati ka makko. O annditi …ďe, kono kam…ďe …ďe paayti mo."
  12,59,"Tuma nde o hebllannoo…ďe doŇčlle ma…ď…ďe …óeen, o maaki: "ngaddanee kam musi…ó…óo mon baaba-gooto. E on nji'aani mi…óo timmina …ďetu ngun, e won¬īde ko mi …ďurdo mo∆ī∆īude e weernoo…ďe …ďen?"(jippinoo…ďr)."
  12,60,"Si on ngaddanaani kam mo, haray …ďetu alanaa on ka am …óoo; wota on …ďado kamm kadi"."
  12,61,"∆Āe mb'i: "min …óa…ď…ďiray mo baba makko, minen ko men golloo…ďe (…óuum)"."
  12,62,"O maakani golloo…ďe makko …ďen: "mba…óee coggeeji(njigguuji) ma…ď…ďe …óin ka doŇčle ma…ď…ďe: belejo'o …ďe ngannditat …ói si …ďe nduttima ka yim…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen, belejo'o …ďe njiiltoto"."
  12,63,"Tuma nde …ďe nduuttinoo ka ben ma…ď…ďe, …ďe mbi'i: "eeheyma ben(baaba) amen, min ska…óaama …ďetu. neldu amen musi…ó…óo amen on, men …ďetanee. Ko men reenoo…ďe mo"."